      <title>丹麦拒绝特朗普向格陵兰岛派遣医疗船的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/22/us/politics/trump-greenland-hospital-ship.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦国防部长表示，格陵兰不需要医疗援助，一天前特朗普总统表示，他计划向该岛派遣一艘“大型医院船”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/22/us/politics/trump-greenland-hospital-ship.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Feb 2026 15:25:28 GMT</pubDate>
